                     <interp inst="t18220417-46-person468" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to Mr. Foulkard, a pawn-broker, of Providence Row, Finsbury Square. -<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182204170023"></xptr>The prisoner came to me on the 24th of March, between twelve and one o'clock, and pawned two black gowns, and a pair of trowers, for 18 s. in the name of 
               <persName id="t18220417-46-person469">
                  John 
                  Bradshaw
               <interp inst="t18220417-46-person469" type="surname" value="Bradshaw"></interp>
